                                         InformerFactory factory,

                                         PropertyProvider provider,
                                         StrategyType strategy)
Construct a gaedo servcie allowing reading/writing to an indexable graph

Parameters:
graph - graph we want to write/read to/from
containedClass - class we want to map to that graph
informerClass - informer used to allow easy queries on that class
factory - informer factory
repository - service repository, to load other classes
provider - property provider
strategy - mapping strategy. If bean based, the bean fields will define which edges are read/written. If graph based, that's the edges that define how the object will be loaded.
